In nonpolarized macrophages , this enhancement of infection by JEV was statistically significant for IL - 33 alone , for IL - 33 combined with TSLP , and for IL - 33 combined with TSLP and IL - 25 ( Fig . 9A ) . In IL - 4 - polarized macrophages , a further enhancement of infection was statistically significant for IL - 25 alone , TSLP alone , and every combination of IL - 33 with the other alarmins ( Fig . 9B ) .
